author: Nineteenth century videos. Back to life.
description:
The year is 1895, and a startling new invention is capturing images of the world in motion. Among the very first short features ever recorded is a fascinating glimpse into the lives of ordinary people engaging with one of the era's most revolutionary devices: the bicycle. 

Music: Tchaikovsky, Op.42-3
